                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-1</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-249&quot; title=&quot;Allow the user to set the upper limit to the thread count on the MDS&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-249&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-249&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; implements a compile time maximum limit on the MDS thread count (instead of hardcoded now), this needs to be mentioned in the section about setting mds thread count if we have one (or if we don&apos;t, we need to create it).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
