                            <comment id="66465" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 12 Sep 2013 07:54:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;During our review for lustre manual chapter 31.9, we found something wrong with &quot;lctl conf_param&quot; to set MDS/OSS thread count and several proc parameter name errors. I discussed with Fanyong about the conf_param problem and will create a lustre ticket to fix it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, I will post a doc patch here to correct those parameter name errors. And due to the conf_param problem, some description still can&apos;t be updated correctly. &lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
